text: Paravelleda gedeensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Adlbauer in 2010. It is known from Kenya.BioLib.cz - Paravelleda gedeensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 2010
